address: Anantagiri Hills, Vikarabad Road, Godamguda, Vikarabad, Hyderabad, Telangana 500038, India
street: Anantagiri Hills, Vikarabad Road, Godamguda, Vikarabad
hotelDescription:
Surrounded by meadows and fields, this relaxed resort is 6 km from the town of Vikarabad and 2 km from Godamgura railway station. It's 7 km from Ananthagiri Hills Viewpoint, offering scenic sunrise and sunset views of the Araku Valley.
 Basic cottages offer porches and en suite bathrooms; some have air-conditioning. Upgraded A-frame cottages add modern decor, sitting areas and verandas. There are no TVs.
 Complimentary perks include 3 meals at a casual open-air restaurant, plus dirt kart and zip line activities. There's also an outdoor pool and a rope park. Trekking and jeep tours are available, as are camping pitches. The resort is alcohol-free.
